reviewText: Awesome to pass your test! Learn it, love it, pass it!

Este DVD es una pelicula y NO tiene control de las preguntas y respuestas.  Parece un DVD que anuncia unas vacaciones en Lake Tahoo Neveda.  Cuidado con este DVD, "NO LO RECOMIENDO".  El vendedor debe REVELAR que solo una pelicula.

I teach people to study for the Citizenship Test and this bilingual DVD is fun for both educators and students.  I highly recommend to get it soon since the new test starts in October.  They also have a web site with update information [...]
